==家庭==
水仙大師的長子奧菲歐·夸利亞塔（Orfeo Quagliata）也是玻璃藝術家，現為墨西哥 Phuze Design 公司首席設計師<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.zongtai.com.tw/chinese/01_case/01_black/04_blog/04_blog_detail.php?sid=27&project=1&cid=1&ccid=17 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2013-06-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115434/http://www.zongtai.com.tw/chinese/01_case/01_black/04_blog/04_blog_detail.php?sid=27&project=1&cid=1&ccid=17 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.phuzedesign.com/Medium/contact.html |title=Biography of Orfeo Quagliata |accessdate=2013-06-25 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304114448/http://www.phuzedesign.com/Medium/contact.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

